{"tid":1840553,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"野味天王 WU-HAN-WU-HAN-CHINA！","createTime":"2020-01-25T01:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:05:09.000Z","uid":81236,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"24fdadb6ab5300ab7c1ff437e840ed4322c189cf","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n野味天王 Mamma Mia<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/183934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/183934</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lWDzsdBqmkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlWDzsdBqmkc&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=e2809e10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lWDzsdBqmkc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【野味天王】<br />\n改自︰美味天王<br />\n<br />\nIntro:<br />\n武漢嚟架，哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈！<br />\n新 SARS 呀~ 野味咁好味架？正到痺呀!<br />\n好好味呀！冇得頂呀！<br />\n<br />\nVerse:<br />\n平凡動物實在食不慣，蝙蝠山雞於每一餐，<br />\n竹鼠刺蝟梅花鹿肉，入急症也會漸覺開懷。<br />\n無懼病毒亦是可怕，沙士教訓暫時忘了吧！<br />\n貓狗配上甜酸苦辣，如若你有四隻腳，我放你上最美的餐盤。<br />\n<br />\nChorus:<br />\n誰令病毒疫情驟生？WU-HAN-WU-HAN-CHINA！<br />\n高燒傷風嘔吐，WU-HAN-CHINA！<br />\n潛伏病毒病人入侵，染上染上這惡病，匆匆一生將快終結！<br />\n<br />\n誰令病毒疫情驟生？WU-HAN-WU-HAN-CHINA！<br />\n高風險的高鐵，WU-HAN-CHINA！<br />\n傳遞疾病忘掉衛生，暖暖那份愛，中港一家始終不會分隔。<br />\n<br />\nOuttro:<br />\n嘩，乜咁啱嘅，一齊入院啦！<br />\n老婆，今晚有野味湯飲呀！<br />\n媽媽，記得煮埋我飯呀！<br />\n唔該一碟蝙蝠刺身，加果子狸添，加多三隻竹鼠。<br />\n加多些少鹿肉伴伴碟呀老細。<br />\n唔該！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SULittleEatGod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSULittleEatGod&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=177af126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SULittleEatGod</a>"},{"pid":"d4bbb7bc1d0d21241c724711da96358870bc2672","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"野味天王 Mamma Mia<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ocdtEfX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ocdtEfX</a><br />\n#470 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a91228ff470bc07f8d488f680008cda4ca49ade9","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:25:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b20c07559001d2925237ee58e7c9c7499403c03a","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91f4650dbbaacd15628b8a5c651e02a60ec7bfd0","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8842adcc887588c8af50240e6c833831b20b7ae3","tid":1840553,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"嘩好野味呀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"744e0e2ac3757fbf0b8ed02292d5032a0fb6f0e3","tid":1840553,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad2605a088408c43c377d3dadcdc069c7137c19","tid":1840553,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"Wuhanwuhan China"},{"pid":"ef73d6a0462a6a057d7632794c87baf8378ec5ad","tid":1840553,"uid":281518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"354ba5ec0169198c82f1ad6387b56e57f649f351","tid":1840553,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:37:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9a769f4289332019148298e3d04e9879702695d","tid":1840553,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"高質<br />\n抽得好應"},{"pid":"b8e17d00ed85b0d15eeefbe9ca44339bde52b39e","tid":1840553,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac